Open kitchen and dining room that leads to the deck. Three spacious bedrooms and a common bathroom complete the main floor living. The lower level offers a large seating area with a fireplace that leads to the backyard. Full bathroom and extra living space that can be a fourth bedroom or in-law suite. This home will not disappoint! Make you appointment today!
